*Nervozan* je čekao rezultate ispita. (He was nervous while waiting for the exam results.)

Njegovo je ponašanje bilo *nervozno*. (His behaviour was nervous.)

*Nervozno* se šalio s prijateljima. (He was nervously joking with his friends.)

Ona je bila *nervozna* dok je čekala rezultate. (She was nervous while waiting for the results.)

On je *nervozno* zakoračio u sobu. (He nervously stepped into the room.)